#

Simple No-Knead Sourdough

60 min
$2.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

Gluten

VegetarianVegan

Cuisine:

Description

Enjoy a crusty, flavorful sourdough bread with minimal effort! Perfect for sandwiches or as a side to your meals.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 3 cups
  • water: 1 1/2 cups
  • active sourdough starter: 1/2 cup
  • salt: 1 1/2 teaspoons
